headline: Duke Energy signs agreements for 2 GW of data centers in past month: CFO
summary: “You're going to see this kind of burst of activity that will be signing contracts that will come to reality in '27, '28, '29, when we see acceleration of load growth,” said Duke Energy’s Brian Savoy.
